      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DR. BEYOND (4) is rarely far away but tends to find one better, placing seven from 15 starts. Finished in the minors latest when third (32.94) at Traralgon and may be close to breaking through. Form here sound including two wins. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Capable of going well again. JUST JEZEBEL (3) was a brilliant winner two back scoring by 1.5 lengths but drifted back latest and safely held when 8th and beaten 13 lengths at Sandown (30.57). Should be about the money. HUGO ROSE (2) has a strong record here with two wins and two placings from five starts. Placed last time (24.87) at this track in a Mix 6/7, finishing second and beaten 6 lengths. Suited here and expected to run well. CALLISTA (5) is likely to have admirers.",
